  "tosSection3Para1": "{appName} is a Zdravie companion application intended for informational and organizational purposes only. The Service is NOT a medical device and does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment recommendations.",
  "tosSection3Para2": "The AI Triage feature provides general guidance based on the Príznaky you report. It is not a substitute for professional medical judgment. Always seek the advice of a qualified healthcare provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay seeking it because of something you read in this Service.",
  "tosSection3Para3": "In a medical ePohotovosť call your local Pohotovosť number (e.g. 911, 112) immediately. Do not rely on the Service for Pohotovosť response.",
  "tosSection4Title": "Využívanie služby",
  "tosSection4Intro": "Súhlasíte, že nebudete:",
  "tosSection4Bullet1": "využívať službu na akékoľvek nezákonné účely;",
  "tosSection4Bullet2": "Pokúšať sa o spätnú analýzu, dekompiláciu alebo disasembláciu aplikácie;",
  "tosSection4Bullet3": "Nahrávať obsah, ktorý je škodlivý, podvodný alebo porušuje práva duševného vlastníctva;",
  "tosSection4Bullet4": "Interfere with the proper functioning of the Service or attempt to access data belonging to Iné users;",
  "tosSection4Bullet5": "Používať službu na zasielanie nevyžiadaných správ alebo spamu.",
  "tosSection5Title": "Predplatné a platby",
  "tosSection5Para1": "Certain features of the Service require a paid subscription (\"PPro or \"EEnterprise plan). Subscription fees are billed monthly through the platform application store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) subject to their respective tPodmienky",
  "tosSection5Para2": "Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. You can manage or Zrušiť your subscription at any Čas through your platform's account sNastavenia",
  "tosSection5Para3": "Poplatky za predplatné môžeme zmeniť po predchádzajúcom primeranom oznámení. Zmeny poplatkov sa nebudú vzťahovať na vaše aktuálne fakturačné obdobie.",
  "tosSection6Title": "Vaše údaje",
  "tosSection6Para1": "You retain ownership of the Zdravie data you submit to the Service. Our use of your data is described in our Súkromie Policy, which is incorporated into these Podmienky by reference.",
  "tosSection6Para2": "You may Exportovať your data at any Čas via the in-app Exportovať feature, and you may permanently Odstrániť your account and Všetko associated data via Nastavenia → Odstrániť Account.",
  "tosSection7Title": "Upozornenia",
  "tosSection7Para1": "SLUŽBA SA POSKYTUJE „TAK, AKO JE“ A „PODĽA DOSTUPNOSTI“ BEZ AKÝCHKOĽVEK ZÁRUK, či už výslovných alebo implicitných, vrátane, ale nie výlučne, implicitných záruk obchodovateľnosti, vhodnosti na konkrétny účel alebo neporušenia práv.",
  "tosSection7Para2": "We do not warrant that the Service will be uninterrupted, error-free, or secure, or that the AI Triage recommendations will be accurate or appropriate for your specific situation.",
  "tosSection8Title": "Obmedzenie zodpovednosti",
  "tosSection8Para1": "TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, IN Nie EVENT SHALL {producer} BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF DATA, ARISING OUT OF OR RELATED TO YOUR USE OF (OR INABILITY TO USE) THE SERVICE, WHETHER BASED ON WARRANTY, CONTRACT, TORT, OR ANY Iné LEGAL THEORY.",
  "tosSection9Title": "Ukončenie",
  "tosSection9Para1": "You may stop using the Service and Odstrániť your account at any Čas via SNastavenia We may suspend or terminate your access to the Service if you violate these Podmienky or if we reasonably believe we are Povinné to do so by law.",
  "tosSection9Para2": "Upon termination, Všetko licenses granted to you will end, and your data will be deleted in accordance with our Súkromie Policy.",
